thread.title: Mary

author: Mary
title: Mary
text: Bought a discounted 'used' paddle - prolite magnum graphite stealth burst. I was pleased with it's condition. My only complaint was that it had a card with it showing the weight of 8.6 oz. for the paddle- heavier than what the model usually is. I was attracted to this model because of it was listed as light weight (6.5-7.5 oz) and it's small grip. I was very surprised this weighed so much.
